{"tid":2395780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【分裂國家及顛覆國家罪刑罰為何 教育局長識唔識答？ 】","createTime":"2021-02-05T06:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T06:44:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f161990bde120cac810f78c2379a2efcc9f9f140","tid":2395780,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"【分裂國家及顛覆國家罪刑罰為何 教育局長識唔識答？ 】<br />\nFeb 5, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VwgfRLk0LY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVwgfRLk0LY0&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=11303865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VwgfRLk0LY0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.3K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n教育局發給學校有關國家安全指引，當中要求小學生知道四種國家安全罪行。眾新聞今日向教育局局長楊潤雄詢問，分裂國家罪及顛覆國家罪的刑罰是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄聽了問題後避答説：「我不是法律專家，我亦不是負責執行法律的官員，所以我唔會答你這個問題。」當記者再追問局長時，楊潤雄則轉答另一名記者的問題。"},{"pid":"0d159e70279bbb7f922370a6de28ef580d43249d","tid":2395780,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"無指定刑罰﹐想判幾多隨心﹐隨時恢復埋死刑"},{"pid":"47fd92ca3e29795ac2fe98b4421695b6da0191aa","tid":2395780,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:15:49.000Z","msg":"我兒仔在外國，唔需要知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e497bcba22e25a5a213d940a92f0666ee33fa0","tid":2395780,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"自己都唔識就要求啲學生識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58c0f1f8f92d1867f5b9450fc05353ce411d8bd","tid":2395780,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"我個仔就冇罪<br />\n人地個仔就睇律政司心情"},{"pid":"091e8ec992433ba344f532f130786460bd7e36b9","tid":2395780,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"正確答案：黨安法嘅罪名只適用於賤民，所以唔需要知"},{"pid":"68b1d7cddbde97fc9297b4f3f63c5548dd8302d3","tid":2395780,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"你個國家係勁既怕咩人批評<br />\n<br />\n你係個國家廢，無自信，先至成日禁人言"}]}